---
description: "Enforce strict TypeScript practices"
globs:
  - "**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Enable `strict` mode in `tsconfig.json`.
- Define interfaces for all structured data.
- Avoid using `any`, `unknown`, or untyped variables.
- Explicitly type the return value of all public functions.
- Avoid `any` even in function prototypes; prefer `unknown` with type guards.
- Use literal types and enums when possible.
